类 Offer

  • 所有已实现的接口:
    com.netflix.fenzo.VirtualMachineLease

    public class Offer
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.netflix.fenzo.VirtualMachineLease
    An adapter class to transform a Mesos resource offer to a Fenzo VirtualMachineLease.

    The default implementation provided by Fenzo isn't compatible with reserved resources. This implementation properly combines resources, e.g. a combination of reserved and unreserved cpus.
